      <h1 class="content-hero-title">The Science of Psychedelics</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">What do we actually know about how psychedelics work — and what can we honestly claim the research shows? This page surveys the neuroscience, the clinical trial landscape, and the ecological dimensions of psychedelic science, with careful attention to what the evidence does and does not support.</p>
    </div>

